&lt;h2&gt;


Conclusion: Health is the Ultimate Developer Productivity Hack ü•ë
&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We spend most of our lives in front of these glowing rectangles. Using a bit of TypeScript and Computer Vision to look after our physical well-being isn't just a fun project‚Äîit's an investment in your career longevity.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Summary of what we built:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Real-time capture&lt;/strong&gt; using Electron and a webcam.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Landmark detection&lt;/strong&gt; via MediaPipe to identify spinal alignment points.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Trigonometric analysis&lt;/strong&gt; to detect slouching.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Audio-visual feedback&lt;/strong&gt; to correct behavior.&lt;/li&gt;
