&lt;p&gt;As an indie developer, I was tired of paying $15+/month for screenshot tools or spending hours in Figma every time I needed App Store screenshots. So I built my own ‚Äî and open-sourced it.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://media2.dev.to/dynamic/image/width=800%2Cheight=%2Cfit=scale-down%2Cgravity=auto%2Cformat=auto/https%3A%2F%2Fdev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fuploads%2Farticles%2Fhai6qnoq68rxkhwr2qvz.png" class="article-body-image-wrapper"&gt;&lt;img src="https://media2.dev.to/dynamic/image/width=800%2Cheight=%2Cfit=scale-down%2Cgravity=auto%2Cformat=auto/https%3A%2F%2Fdev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fuploads%2Farticles%2Fhai6qnoq68rxkhwr2qvz.png" alt="Appshots screenshot" width="800" height="502"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;üîó &lt;strong&gt;Live Demo:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;a href="https://appshots.appstate.xyz/" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;appshots.appstate.xyz&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;üì¶ &lt;strong&gt;GitHub:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;a href="https://github.com/oyeolamilekan/appshots" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;github.com/oyeolamilekan/appshots&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;


What is it?
&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A browser-based editor that lets you create professional, high-converting screenshots for the Apple App Store and Google Play Store in minutes. No accounts. No cloud. No tracking. Everything runs locally in your browser.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;


Features
&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;


üì± Device Frames
&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;6 realistic device mockups&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî iPhone 15 Pro Max, iPhone 15 Pro, iPhone 14, iPad Pro 12.9", Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra, Samsung Galaxy Tab S9&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Multiple color options&lt;/strong&gt; per device ‚Äî Black Titanium, Natural, Blue, White, and more&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Flat 2D &amp;amp; 3D rendering modes&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî toggle between a classic frame and a perspective 3D view with visible device edges&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;3D rotation controls&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî adjust Rotate Y and Rotate X for the perfect angle&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Accurate camera elements&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî Dynamic Island, notch, and punch-hole matching each device&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;


üé® Backgrounds &amp;amp; Appearance
&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Solid color backgrounds&lt;/strong&gt; with a full color picker&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;6 gradient presets&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî Sunset, Ocean, Mint, Berry, Royal, Rose&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Global text color picker&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;


üìù Rich Text &amp;amp; Fonts
&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Rich text editor&lt;/strong&gt; for headlines and subheadlines ‚Äî bold, italic, underline, text color, alignment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Google Fonts integration&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî search and preview hundreds of fonts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Independent sizing&lt;/strong&gt; for headline and subheadline&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Width control&lt;/strong&gt; per text block&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Drag-to-reposition&lt;/strong&gt; text anywhere on the canvas&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;


üñºÔ∏è Overlay Images
&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Unlimited overlay images&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî upload badges, logos, arrows, or decorations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Drag, resize, and rotate&lt;/strong&gt; each image independently&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Layer management&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî place behind or in front of the device, reorder freely&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Per-image shadow&lt;/strong&gt; with color, blur, and offset controls&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;


üìê Layout &amp;amp; Positioning
&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;8 position presets&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî Centered, Bleed Bottom, Bleed Top, Float Center, Float Bottom, Tilt Left, Tilt Right, Perspective&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Device size&lt;/strong&gt; slider (scale %)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Device vertical position&lt;/strong&gt; slider (offset %)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Device shadow&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî toggle on/off with color, blur, and vertical offset controls&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;


üìã Project Management
&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Multiple projects&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî create, rename, switch between, and delete&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Auto-save&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî all settings persist to localStorage across sessions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Reset to defaults&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî clear everything and start fresh&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;


üì¶ Export
&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Batch export&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî export all screenshots at once (ZIP for multiple, PNG for single)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;4 export size presets&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî 6.7" iPhone, 6.5" iPhone, 5.5" iPhone, 12.9" iPad Pro&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Full 3D support&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî perspective, edges, and shadows preserved in exports&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Pixel-perfect&lt;/strong&gt; output matching the on-screen preview&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;


üñ•Ô∏è Editor Experience
&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Multi-screenshot gallery&lt;/strong&gt; with horizontal carousel&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Real-time preview&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî all changes update instantly&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Drag-and-drop&lt;/strong&gt; repositioning on the canvas&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Element selection&lt;/strong&gt; with visual feedback&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dark mode UI&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;


How to use it
&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Select a device&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî pick from iPhones, iPads, or Samsung devices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Upload a screenshot&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî add your app's screenshot to the device screen&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Edit text&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî add headlines and subheadlines, format with the rich text toolbar&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Pick a font&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî browse Google Fonts for the perfect typeface&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Set a background&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî choose a solid color or gradient&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Position the device&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî use presets or manually adjust size, position, rotation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Switch to 3D&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî toggle 3D mode and tweak perspective angles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Add overlays&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî upload badges or logos and layer them around the device&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Export&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî download all screenshots at App Store resolution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;

