üîó Try it here
&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://pramit-mandal-ai.netlify.app/" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;üëâ Click here to launch the AI Portfolio&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

